products.description:
"Utilizing 3D NAND Flash and a high-speed SMI controller, this compact
ADATA Ultimate SU800 M.2 2280  solid state drive provides capacities up to 1TB and greatly enhances performance, efficiency, and reliability over traditional 2D NAND.
It also comes with intelligent SLC Caching and a DRAM Cache to boost read/write performance. Featuring LDPC ECC, high TBW (total bytes written), and DEVSLP (Device Sleep),
ADATA Ultimate SU800 M.2 2280  instantly upgrades notebook and desktop PCs with superior stability, durability, and power efficiency."
